  <summary date="2021-06-29T13:47:30Z" status="Introduced in Senate">This bill requires the&#160;Department of Transportation and the Department&#160;of Energy&#160;to jointly establish a working group to make recommendations on the development, adoption, and integration of certain electric vehicles into&#160;U.S. transportation and energy systems. In addition, the working group must develop, electronically publish, and update a resource guide that provides information&#160;about electric vehicles and their&#160;charging infrastructure.</summary>
